'''''Riccix's Revised Basic Holodictionary''''' was an encyclopedia published by [[Riccix]]. Unlike most other dictionaries, ''Riccix's'' did not feature an image of [[Jabba Desilijic Tiure/Legends|Jabba]] the [[Hutt/Legends|Hutt]] in its entry on Hutts. Rather, it featured an image of [[Ka'Pa]] the Hutt, as the editors argued that they were sick of seeing Jabba as the main reference to Hutts in dictionaries. The image of Ka'Pa was taken by the famous [[Holographer/Legends|holographer]], [[Bovit Leebo]].

